    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what \"real\" life? there's nothing left underneath. it's not like i can just reinvent myself or something. when you lose the thing that everyone actually valued about you, you realize there was nothing else there to begin with. it just feels empty. like the whole thing is a mistake.",
