    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a new beginning though. it just feels like the end. like the person they liked is gone and there isn't enough left of me to make it worth staying. it's hard to see a point in dragging this empty thing around when the version of me that mattered is already dead.",
